msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/name"
msgid "Battle of Villers-Bocage [SKIRMISH]"
msgstr "Batalla de Villers-Bocage [ESCARAMUZA]"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/name_big"
msgid "Battle of Villers-Bocage"
msgstr "Batalla de Villers-Bocage"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/story"
msgid ""
"You have been on the ground in Normandy for a week now. \n"
"\n"
" The city of Caen proves to be a tough nut to crack; the Germans have dug in "
"on its North side, beating back every attack so far. \n"
"\n"
"However, near the village of Villers- Bocage an opportunity suddenly "
"presents itself.\n"
"\n"
"You must seize this opportunity and attack Villers-Bocage from the West. "
"Break through any defenses you might find. \n"
"\n"
" Speed is of the essence; we must capture Villers-Bocage before the Germans "
"have time to recover!"
msgstr ""
"Llevas una semana en Normandía. La ciudad de Caen está resultando ser un "
"hueso duro de roer; los alemanes se han atrincherado en su lado norte y han "
"repelido todos los ataques hasta ahora. Sin embargo, cerca del pueblo de "
"Villers-Bocage se presenta una oportunidad.\n"
"\n"
"Debes aprovecharla y atacar Villers-Bocage desde el oeste. Rompe todas las "
"defensas que encuentres. La rapidez es fundamental: ¡debemos capturar "
"Villers-Bocage antes de que los alemanes tengan tiempo de recuperarse!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/place"
msgid "7th Armoured Division, XXX Corps"
msgstr "7.ª División Blindada, XXX Cuerpo"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/date"
msgid "June 13th, 1944 · Outskirts of Villers-Bocage, Normandy, France"
msgstr "13 de junio de 1944 · Afueras de Villers-Bocage, Normandía, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Wizard job, chaps! As a result of your energetic attack, the German "
"positions in and around Caen are now compromised. You exploited this gap "
"very well, this will do wonders for your reputation! "
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo, muchachos! Gracias a vuestro enérgico ataque, las posiciones "
"alemanas en Caen y sus alrededores están ahora comprometidas. Habéis "
"aprovechado muy bien esta oportunidad, ¡esto hará maravillas por vuestra "
"reputación! "

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/outro_failed"
msgid "This is a terrible result for us"
msgstr "Este es un resultado terrible para nosotros."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/outro_failed_hq"
msgid ""
"That borders on disaster. We failed to secure a win, you need to go back and "
"get another effort going!"
msgstr ""
"Eso roza el desastre. No hemos conseguido la victoria, ¡tienes que volver y "
"esforzarte más!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Debes mantener tu cuartel general de campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/mission_ace"
msgid "You must knock Wittmann's Tiger tank out!"
msgstr "¡Debes destruir el tanque Tiger de Wittmann!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/mission_attack"
msgid "Punch a hole in the enemy position and drive north!"
msgstr "¡Abre una brecha en la posición enemiga y avanza hacia el norte!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 German positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados han asegurado %1%/7 posiciones alemanas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome back to the front line, Lieutenant! This is our field HQ, it must "
"remain in our control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido de nuevo al frente, teniente! Este es nuestro cuartel general de "
"campaña, ¡debe permanecer bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Operation Perch is in full swing, a swift assault is necessary to breach "
"through the German lines."
msgstr ""
"La Operación Perch está en pleno apogeo, es necesario un ataque rápido para "
"romper las líneas alemanas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"Be quick, be decisive, and try not to lose too many men! Use the terrain to "
"your advantage."
msgstr ""
"¡Sé rápido, sé decisivo y trata de no perder demasiados hombres! Aprovecha "
"el terreno a tu favor."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"More reinforcements will become available as you progress with your assault!"
msgstr ""
"¡A medida que avances en tu asalto, tendrás más refuerzos a tu disposición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/wittman_1"
msgid "...possible targets! forward..."
msgstr "...¡posibles objetivos! Adelante..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/"
"allied_enemy_ace_near"
msgid "Bloody hell! A Tiger tank!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea! ¡Un tanque Tiger!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/"
"player_enemy_ace_near"
msgid "For Christ’s sake, take cover and flank him. We must defeat him!"
msgstr ""
"Por el amor de Dios, ponte a cubierto y flanquéalo. ¡Debemos derrotarlo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Gentlemen! Germans are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr ""
"¡Señores! ¡Los alemanes están cerca de nuestro cuartel general de campaña!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/allied_enemy_plane"
msgid "Enemy plane!!!"
msgstr "¡Avión enemigo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/allied_enemy_plane2"
msgid "German aircraft inbound!"
msgstr "¡Avión alemán entrando en tu espacio aéreo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "We must hold our command post! There is no room for surrender!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos mantener nuestro puesto de mando! ¡No hay lugar para la rendición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr "¡Comandante! Ahora puedes solicitar un ataque aéreo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/tasks/secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/tasks/"
"secret01_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective #1: Cooked! - eliminated German tank by ammunition cook off."
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto n.º 1: ¡Olla a presión! - Eliminaste un tanque alemán "
"mediante la detonación de municiones."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/tasks/secret02"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 2"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_07_13_villers-bocage_skirmish/tasks/"
"secret02_completed"
msgid "Secret objective #2: Carjacked! - stolen German light vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto n.º 2: ¡Robo de coche! - Vehículo ligero alemán robado."
